How do I receive a replacement identification (ID) card?</h3></div>
				<div class=3D"answer"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Contact Customer service at 410-424-4450 or 1-800-261-2393; or request o=
ne online, through your <a href=3D"https://ehp.healthtrioconnect.com/app/in=
dex.page?" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">HealthLINK account=
</a>. Please allow 7-10 business days for your ID card to arrive.</p>
