How do I change my Primary Care Physician (PCP)?</h3></div>
				<div class=3D"answer"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>You can change your PCP by calling an EHP Customer Service Representativ=
e at <a href=3D"tel:8002612393">1-800-261-2393</a> or <a href=3D"tel:410424=
4450">410-424-4450</a>. You can also change or designate your PCP by loggin=
g into your <a href=3D"https://ehp.healthtrioconnect.com/app/index.page?" t=
arget=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">HealthLink account</a>. Your a=
pproved PCP change will become effective the day EHP is notified.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
